dct_description_sm: At head of title: Société de géographie de Finlande. Running title: Fennia, 30. This edition of the text differs from that which appeared as no. 30 in the series ""Fennia"" in that it was issued without series t.-p.; the atlas is the same as the one which accompanies the series edition (in French) Bibliographies at the end of the description of each map.
Texte: I. Nature (cartes nos. 1-23) II. Population et civilisation (cartes nos. 24-55)--Atlas (2 p. l., iii, 7 p. 55 double pl. (maps, charts, diagrs.))
